data.meta_description: Mieszko I King of Poland was born about 0922 in Poznan, Poland, son of Ziemomysl Prince of Poland. He was married in 1st wife to Unknown First Wife, they gave birth to 1 child. He was married about 0965 in 2nd wife to Dubrawka of Bohemia, they had 3 children. He was married after 0977 in 3rd wife to Oda von Haldensleben. He died on May 25, 992 in Poznan, Poland. This information is part of Genealogy Wylie by Kin Mapper on Genealogy Online.
